videos.headline: TCU QB runs in 9-yard TD
videos.description: Shawn Robinson runs in his second touchdown of the game to put TCU up 31-0 over Southern.

videos.headline: Southern WR outraces TCU defenders for 55-yard TD
videos.description: Southern's John Lampley finds Cameron Mackey wide open down the sideline to get on the board.

videos.headline: Robinson's 3rd TD pass extends TCU's lead
videos.description: Shawn Robinson throws his third touchdown pass of the day to Jalen Reagor from 12 yards out.

videos.headline: TCU scores on 73-yard punt return
videos.description: TCU's Derius Davis takes the punt return 73 yards for his second touchdown of the day.

videos.headline: TCU backup QB converts 57-yard TD pass
videos.description: TCU backup quarterback Michael Collins finds TreVontae Hights for a 57-yard touchdown.
